    "title": "Prayer for the Interment of Sacred Writing in a Genizah, by Morah Yehudis Fishman",
    "author": "Yehudis Fishman",
    "coauthors": [
        {
            "name": "Yehudis Fishman",
            "bio": "I have been teaching Torah and Chassidic writings for over forty years to students of all ages and backgrounds, both on the East Coast and the Midwest. I have been a director of several Jewish organizations in Santa Fe and Colorado. My articles and poetry on a wide variety of Jewish topics have been printed in many publications, and also are available online.",
